that was the English horn.

44
00:03:23.840 --> 00:03:24.770
Ironically, of course,

45
00:03:24.770 --> 00:03:30.010
the English horn is neither a horn, it's
not a brass instrument, nor is it English.

46
00:03:30.010 --> 00:03:34.270
It's a woodwind instrument,
a low oboe of French origin.

47
00:03:34.270 --> 00:03:37.310
