55
00:05:09.913 --> 00:05:14.870
to balance them more strings were needed,
and a bigger string sound.

56
00:05:14.870 --> 00:05:18.870
The string instruments themselves,
they didn't get bigger, but

57
00:05:18.870 --> 00:05:21.960
how they were constructed did change.

58
00:05:21.960 --> 00:05:23.650
Let's look at the slide of a violin here.

59
00:05:23.650 --> 00:05:29.610
First of all, notice with the Baroque
violin that the finger board on the left

60
00:05:30.760 --> 00:05:36.770
is on the same plane, same flat plane,
