it's gotten larger in the 19th century.

65
00:05:55.070 --> 00:05:59.090
And the horse hair would make up
the sounding part of the bow, well,

66
00:05:59.090 --> 00:06:03.780
that has gotten wider and
the steel rod is placed inside,

67
00:06:03.780 --> 00:06:09.700
that makes it possible to tighten the bow
and increase pressure on the strings.

68
00:06:09.700 --> 00:06:15.450
